data.description:
Charming 3 Bedroom Cape Cod Home with Finished Basement

Welcome to your dream Cape Cod home! This charming 3-bedroom home offers the perfect blend of classic Cape Cod architecture and modern comforts. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this property is a haven for those seeking both style and functionality. Spacious and well-appointed, each bedroom provides ample space for relaxation and rest. The fully finished basement is a versatile space, perfect for a family room or home office. The possibilities are endless, and it adds valuable square footage to your living space. Kitchen boasts lovely updated granite countertops. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, you're just minutes away from schools, parks, shopping, and all the amenities you need.
.This home has been lovingly maintained and is move-in ready, allowing you to start enjoying the Cape Cod lifestyle immediately.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this home gem your own. With its spacious interior, finished basement, and picturesque surroundings, it's the perfect place to call home. Schedule your showing today and experience the Cape Cod lifestyle at its finest.
